{
  "stem": "27507.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were maybe 12, 14, maybe even older.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were discussing if I was Jewish, or not Jewish, and if to call a policeman or not to call a policeman.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, finally-- so I was withdrawing in the direction of the line-- the street car-- the tramway line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the tramway came, I jumped onto the tram.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- I think that they did it so that they didn't manage to jump onto that tram.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I thought they might have jumped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I thought they might have jumped to tram immediately following.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In short, I was so terrified that I-- first, I climbed under one of the benches, and was-- and then I got out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was all the time for-- must have been for hours after, completely certain that they were following me, that they were-- I was in a state completely paranoid, thinking that they were behind me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were in a train behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were searching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were somewhere here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were somewhere there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I didn't go out of the tram.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That that must have happened at maybe 3:00 or 4:00 in the afternoon, probably even earlier, because we ate lunch at 1:00 or so, maybe 3:00.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't leave the tram.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the conductor didn't even ask me for a ticket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the tram was going from one end to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It must have taken every time three quarters of an hour or longer to go from one end of the line to another.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so it went until 9:00 in the evening, when it was the police hour, curfew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You couldn't after that move in Warsaw after 9:00.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "If you moved in the street, you were dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They would shoot you.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
